channel.title: Crashed Remastered - LilBoi [drum step]
channel.description:
I made the original version of this track over one year ago when I had just downloaded the first version of Auxy which had the green logo. I had made couple tracks before this but I wasn’t sure if I liked Auxy yet. There was something in this certain track that I liked very much back then and still do. I don’t really know what it is because this song isn’t very versatile and it’s not the best one I have made, but there was still something in it what made me fall in love with Auxy.
Crashed remastered on soundcloud here: https://soundcloud.com/lil_poi/crashed-remastered ![image|567x500](upload://d2WTWU09MSIbCEp83Wb0AkLQgQz.jpeg)
Original version on Youtube here: https://youtu.be/_M8U9IMSLBQ
